{"type":"message","id":"64848be7","parentId":"a8609161","timestamp":"2026-06-10T07:18:49.405Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the top products from Vietnam hair clip category:\n\n1. **Hàn Quốc Hình Chữ U Tóc Nữ Mới Phong Cách Trung Quốc** - Product ID: 29884050416, Price: 16,000 VND, SalesCount: 984, 7D: 99, Growth: 0%, Rating: 4.74\n2. **Kẹp tóc càng cua cặp tóc càng cua size lớn 13cm hình vuông** - Product ID: 25395566794, Price: 17,600 VND, SalesCount: 961, 7D: 0, Growth: 0%, Rating: 4.88\n\n\n3. **GOTI Kẹp Tóc Trung Niên Hình Bông Hoa Nhiều Mẫu** - Product ID: 24270554853, Price: 78,750 VND, SalesCount: 950, 7D: 34, Growth: 0.74%, Rating: 4.87\n4. **Kẹp Tóc / Kẹp Càng Cua To Lớn 15cm Acrylic** - Product ID: 26236221321, Price: 5,000 VND, SalesCount: 929\n\n, 7D: 217, Growth: 13.29%, Rating: 4.31\n5. **Kẹp tóc nơ voan siêu phổng** - Product ID: 41708549277, Price: 42,000 VND, SalesCount: 920, 7D: 259, Growth: 4.19%, Rating: 5.00\n6. **Set 12 kẹp càng cua** - Product ID: 14614971699, Price: 12,000 VND, SalesCount: 908, 7D: 120, Growth: 0%, Rating: 4.86\n7. **Trâm Cài Tóc Bằng Gỗ Phong Cách Trung Hoa Cổ Điển** - Product ID: 25610238614, Price: 10,000 VND, SalesCount: 836, 7D: 273, Growth: 31.65%, Rating: 4.76\n8. **Hàn Quốc Size Lớn Thanh Lịch Nữ Bé Gái** - Product ID: 27722060243, Price: 17,499 VND, SalesCount: 807, 7D: 189, Growth: 0%, Rating: 4.77\n9. **Kẹp tóc hình cá mập cỡ lớn màu đen mờ 15cm** - Product ID: 49704658936, Price: 18,900 VND, SalesCount: 758, 7D: 196, Growth: 10.66%, Rating: 4.80\n\nI'm reviewing the top performers across different hair clip styles and price points, noting which ones have the strongest growth momentum and customer ratings. The wooden Chinese-style hair stick is showing exceptional growth at over 31%, while the Korean large-sized clips maintain consistent sales volume despite no growth. Tiếp tục kiểm tra sản phẩm với mức giá thấp hơn này trên 1688 để xác nhận nguồn gốc và kh