{"type":"message","id":"3d132531","parentId":"d5175d33","timestamp":"2026-06-10T07:19:05.525Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now I have the tool list. I can use:\n- `ali1688_similar_product` to search 1688 for similar products\n- `tiktok_similar_product` to search TikTok VN for similar products\n- `tiktok_product_trend` for TikTok trend data\n- `tiktok_product_video_author` for TikTok video/author data\n\nLet me now:\n1. Get the TikTok trend for the wooden hair stick product (Product ID: 25610238614)\n2. Search 1688 for the same/similar product\n3. Search TikTok VN for similar products to this category\n\nLet me focus on the product with best growth - the wooden hair stick (木簪/Trâm Cài Tóc Bằng Gỗ Phong Cách Trung Hoa Cổ Điển Mới) - Product ID 25610238614 on Shopee, Price: 10,000 VND, SalesCount: 836, 7D: 273, MonthlyGrowth: 31.65%.\n\n\nThe 10,000 VND price point is problematic since it converts to only $0.40, which falls well short of the $1.50 minimum threshold needed to maintain a 70% gross margin after accounting for the roughly 45% in fixed costs.\n\nLet me reconsider the pricing strategy for the Vietnamese market—it's a budget-conscious region, so I should be targeting higher-margin products rather than volume leaders. Looking back at the earlier entries, I notice several with better growth rates like the 13.29% and 4.19% gains, though those might also be priced too low to be profitable. I need to find products that balance reasonable sales velocity with sufficient markup room.\n","thinkingSignature":"ffff5d810bfcec1c0df6c944042d1c96f121e174f7673a3e619ddabf4e54d707"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f41ed63912ac48b9abef94bd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\" \\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"tiktok_similar_product\",\"arguments\":{\"searchName\":\"hair clip claw clip Vietnam\",\"page\":1,\"site\":\"VN\"}},\"id\":6}'"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dd6c0d83ed6e45cd839c78a9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\" \\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"tiktok_similar_product\",\"arguments\":{\"searchName\":\"kẹp tóc càng cua hair clip\",\"page\":1,\"site\":\"VN\"}},\"id\":7}'"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":30817,"output":636,"cacheRead":71488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102941,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781075937236,"responseId":"067842e1db15a29f83ac45b5602eac74"}}
