{"type":"message","id":"369b74a2","parentId":"d95f1ff5","timestamp":"2026-06-10T07:19:58.364Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! Now I have the full trend data for the SÂU HOUSE 6-tooth claw clip:\n\n**Product**: [MUA 1 TẶNG 1] Kẹp tắc càng cua 6 Răng SÂUHOUSE\n**TikTok Product ID**: 1732311961339659361\n**Price**: 49,000 VND (~$1.96)\n**Weekly sales**: ~1,000-1,772 (very stable)\n**Monthly sales**: ~4,375\n**Rating**: 4.80 (consistent)\n\n\n**Reviews**: Growing from 946 in Feb to 2,409 by Jun, with no significant price fluctuations throughout the period. The sales volume has proven remarkably stable over the past 4 months, averaging between 931-1,772 units weekly. I'm now calculating the gross margin based on a 1688 cost estimate of ¥3-5 per set.\n\nEven at the higher end of my cost estimate, the margins are exceptional—ranging from 166% down to 278%—which far exceeds the 70% threshold I need. This product is clearly a winner. Now I'm working on constructing the TikTok shop link for Vietnam, which requires the shop ID and product ID. I'm analyzing which claw clip is the better opportunity—either the 5-tooth option at 49,000 VND with 17,431 reviews and 832 weekly sales, or the 6-tooth variant. Let me retrieve the product details for the 5-tooth version to make a final comparison.\n\nI realize now that the first product ID I found is actually for the 6-tooth claw clip at 49,000 VND with 4.8 stars, and I have the direct TikTok link to access it. Let me compile the full TikTok product and shop links for Vietnam to give you the complete picture.\n\nLooking at the profit margins on this SÂU HOUSE claw clip, the selling price is 49,000 VND (roughly $1.96 USD), and if I source it from 1688 at around ¥3 per set, the gross margin after accounting for goods cost comes to about 73.8% before platform fees. Even with the 45% fixed cost allocation for Vietnam operations, I'd still be looking at solid profitability at that price point. 73.8% > 70% ✅\n\nSo the SÂU HOUSE 6-tooth claw clip passes the profit margin check. Now I'm writing this finding to the Feishu spreadsheet to track it, but I need to verify the bot has edit permissions on that bitable first.\n","thinkingSignature":"fc08f3142ac7a57194d686654fc8c1812313d520e358ba7f1ce8f4a0345e6dc4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了一款非常稳定的利润款。让我写入飞书多维表格并汇报给你。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9a3fa7237bbf4d64a1728ec8","name":"feishu_bitable_app_table_record","arguments":{"action":"list","app_token":"AKppbA…QnZd","table_id":"tblHU2do30jzinJT","filter":{"conjunction":"and","conditions":[{"field_name":"商品名称","operator":"contains","value":["SÂU HOUSE"]}]}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1836,"output":684,"cacheRead":126624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781075990741,"responseId":"06784317468bd6ea13c11260ba21ad61"}}
