ual net profit would be 46,600 VND times 0.55, which is around 25,630 VND per unit or roughly $1.02 per unit after all costs are deducted. Now I'll write up the findings for the user and log this to the Feishu bitable.\n","thinkingSignature":"13867d459ef86edfd13471bdd8995323c4928958182f023307ea88470f08229d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_067629468a504170afdf569f","name":"feishu_bitable_app_table_record","arguments":{"action":"create","app_token":"AKppbA…QnZd","table_id":"tblHU2do30jzinJT","fields":{"1688价格(CNY)":"","三级类目":"Hair Claws","产品连接":"https://shop.tiktok.com/en/product/1732311961339659361","估利润":10200,"商品名称":"[MUA 1 TẶNG 1] Kẹp tắc càng cua 6 Răng SÂUHOUSE Cặp tóc Kẹp càng cua Hàn Quốc thời trang Kẹp tắc nữ hot trend","推荐等级":"A级","采集状态":"已采集","增长率":8.5,"站点":"越南","行动建议":"正常采购首选30-50件","售价（本地货币）":49000,"利润率(%)":77,"选品来源":["Sorftime-TK数据"],"IP风险":"无","月销量":4375}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2684,"output":868,"cacheRead":129728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133280,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781076010968,"responseId":"0678432bd7ecd9314e5e918863d86216"}}
